{"tid":162501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[盡力秒回] 原來身邊冇哂朋友既感覺..","createTime":"2017-03-19T10:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T15:12:27.000Z","uid":19863,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70706b72af59385abfa1172ae570d9d4ac03dc3f","tid":162501,"uid":19863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:45:24.000Z","msg":"首先,唔係5p徵友 post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開post原因,因為最近同女朋友分開左<br />\n我發現呢一年幾以來<br />\n慢慢放棄左好多野, 包括身邊既朋友<br />\n從前我既世界就只有佢一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當失去既時候,回望一下呢段日子<br />\n原來我放棄左太多, 原來我好怕一個人<br />\n原來我好怕安靜<br />\n近排冇哂自己既生活<br />\n覺得自己安靜到就快頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望係連登搵到D自己一個發呆<br />\n又冇乜朋友,又冇乜喜好既人<br />\n<br />\n我好樂意秒回, 傾乜都好, 講乜都好<br />\n希望有人都願意同我傾下計<br />\n下面留言 , 如果有私人事想傾都可以<br />\ntgid: twmat<br />\n<br />\n未休息既任何時間都可以盡快回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5affaf55f9588c9fddd298e0f88ae06417386e","tid":162501,"uid":19863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"我都知星期日好多人都忙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfaab0d7129a0e07d4758e4dcb54e8df98249fc5","tid":162501,"uid":70007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:48:03.000Z","msg":"我都係咁既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8ec5698abbe585c5a324fecc2648acb7f846a0","tid":162501,"uid":19154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:48:12.000Z","msg":"幾歲"},{"pid":"c36ed7c99e50725a08e6368ab5d14cb6f078baa4","tid":162501,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,