 /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家一樣，個個都話我大把朋友<br />\n<br />\n結論係WhatsApp 壞左<br />\n無人搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電話壞左<br />\n無人主動約我食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99fba91410e08b3c42115780fa371fb9b5ef6e4","tid":162501,"uid":19863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有同感嗎</blockquote><br />\n以前識落果啲朋友 自己無刻意去keep contact <br />\n一出黎做野就好多都自然流失哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前番工既同事, 果刻好開心<br />\n玩到好close<br />\n但係又因為自己傻仔<br />\n離開左佢地個圈子 唉好後悔"},{"pid":"a66fb290e236bcf672f19c5c6ad81378bc24301b","tid":162501,"uid":19863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身d朋友係因為之前掛住拍拖冇理到佢地<br />\n所以疏遠左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實拍拖果一刻,都仲未離開圈子<br />\n因為女朋友都認識佢地, 直到慢慢2個人離開<br />\n自己2個傻傻地 每日面對對方<br />\n就係咁,不知不覺開心而日子就過左成年"},{"pid":"49c56594a304805051158ec2995dc0e924cb5cdb","tid":162501,"uid":59543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"自我覺得  朋友會覺自己麻煩 唔敢再揾 其實我都想同人見面傾計 食糖水咩都好 唔想一收工就返屋企on99睇波 我都好想有朋友會知道真實 ge我 會扶起我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37b704eb46769d349dfa53f87cb1cdc4e2a59a5","tid":162501,"uid":46893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:00:14.000Z","msg":"自己一個食緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class