落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ca7f57b9e09bf44e971bd0e280577bdca830d4","tid":162501,"uid":19863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>吾識講野<br />\n<br />\n無咩朋友+1</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔知點樣再搵到新既朋友<br />\n新既圈子, 係人地既眼中我係一個好樂觀<br />\n好開朗既人, 但係其實我真係冇朋友<br />\n但好似佢地唔會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家一樣，個個都話我大把朋友<br />\n<br />\n結論係WhatsApp 壞左<br />\n無人搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電話壞左<br />\n無人主動約我食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日比人誤以為有朋友真係好難受"},{"pid":"d4ee42dd4d55b19f42d3d9ce8155745998a02414","tid":162501,"uid":48483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吾識講野<br />\n<br />\n無咩朋友+1</blockquote><br />\n吾你老母死返5p啦on9仔"},{"pid":"af1dda597837d005d5b6563725f60c4f96ca2aee","tid":162501,"uid":14479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:11:53.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲都係人生嘅經驗嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愛一個上一課<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你之後睇翻就會覺得冇呢啲經歷你就唔會係你<br />\n加油啊樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93633779ca1d5b1cbe562a0c902d1d5f42826471","tid":162501,"uid":19863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自我覺得  朋友會覺自己麻煩 唔敢再揾 其實我都想同人見面傾計 食糖水咩都好 唔想一收工就返屋企on99睇波 我都好想有朋友會知道真實 ge我 會扶起我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打 其實朋友既關係 <br />\n我諗唔需要太介意自己有幾麻煩<br />\n朋友有好多種, 有d會陪你<br />\n講好說話既朋友, 有d仆街既講難聽既你聽<br />\n但係當下你就係需要呢一班朋友<br />\n一齊開心 都只係過程之一<br />\n<br />\n我諗我都係, 好多人以前會講<br />\n我係一個收埋自己既人, 就算幾開心<br />\n嘻嘻哈哈, 但都總係睇唔透我<br />\n原因唔係佢地唔主動了解<br />\n係我唔打開呢對牆 呢對門<br />\n佢地唔會封鎖對你既感情<br />\n但係你同朋友之間既友誼<br />\n應該要自己去努力<br />\n我係咁諗<br />\n(可惜我冇對像 冇朋友)"},{"pid":"12e1aef4efb72d123edd673618afff6d4b773bc9","tid":162501,"uid":19863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:25:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己一個食緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前自己一個食會覺老尷 但已成了習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以前成日都好白痴<br />\n覺得自己落去食會比人睇住<br />\n但最近我都自己去食飯<br />\n唉... 根本就冇人會在意我"},{"pid":"0e93de7572aeb59e42f4b36c0f55816bf6a905a3","tid":162501,"uid":19863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:25:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重色輕友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對唔住啊...<br />\n我好努力改變緊..."},{"pid":"419ca5e52f1875332ead0e2b19dd4e6e05b44210","tid":162501,"uid":19863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係咁  <br />\n4個月前分開左之後  發現自己乜都冇</blockquote><br />\n你現在過得好嗎?<br />\n你放低未啊?</blockquote><br />\n都好番7788 啦  <br />\n<br />\n過得一般  仍然捱緊</blockquote><br />\n我每一晚都訓唔好<br />\n訓2-3個鐘就會發夢見到佢醒<br />\n開心到甜到醒又有<br />\n佢叫我離開佢既又有<br />\n精神好差啊..."},{"pid":"37151d2fdfb3f3373458e38f960f9ef0ba75b3e9","tid":162501,"uid":46893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己一個食緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前自己一個食會覺老尷 但已成了習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以前成日都好白痴<br />\n覺得自己落去食會比人睇住<br />\n但最近我都自己去食飯<br />\n唉... 根本就冇人會在意我</blockquote><br />\n雖然都自己一個食左咁耐 但都係好唔習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8812893266c67287369b6e9f5e7d9d02dd12a9de","tid":162501,"uid":46893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:27:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己一個食緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前自己一個食會覺老尷 但已成了習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以前成日都好白痴<br />\n覺得自己落去食會比人睇住<br />\n但最近我都自己去食飯<br />\n唉... 根本就冇人會在意我</blockquote><br />\n雖然都自己一個食左咁耐 但都係好唔習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果衣家有女朋友仔同我一齊食就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b112e0e47a748c8828ee2c7d225c9380a10a722","tid":162501,"uid":91012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>吾識講野<br />\n<br />\n無咩朋友+1</blockquote><br />\n吾你老母死返5p啦on9仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求教學"},{"pid":"0044bcd7dc7140aa7fc209f73a4dec415b1e6362","tid":162501,"uid":4727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:28:52.000Z","msg":"巴打同女朋友一齊幾耐？<br />\n本身冇興趣？平時冇social開 ？"},{"pid":"686b60c98315eb67c6477eba77933a9aa58fb5fc","tid":162501,"uid":19863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我曾經都有兩個好好的朋友<br />\n但經歷一些事後 似乎我們之間已經回不去好朋友的關係了。<br />\n秒回的whatsapp 無盡的白痴話題....<br />\n現在幾日才一個<br />\n有時候再想能回到當初就好 可惜不能了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好好既朋友我以前都有一位<br />\n佢比我年齡大小小<br />\n但係佢好成熟, 我初中果陣認識佢<br />\n佢教左我好多<br />\n佢會提點我, 佢見證住我<br />\n拍拖, 分開, 拍拖 分開<br />\n失業, 工作 又失業<br />\n但上年鬧左一場交, 我地既感覺都唔同曬了"},{"pid":"2cd4ddbddee1bb10b77ed96c67233b04fba55070","tid":162501,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" cla